pr_title: Upgraded ELK to 7.13.2 and Configured the Filebeat Suricata module
pr_body:
#20 
Upgraded Elasticseach, Logstash, Filebeat and Kibana to 7.13.2 and tested following:
- [x] Importing kibana.ndjson and see if it still compatbile for lastest kibana.
- [x] Runnig pcaps and see if the log data are being imported correctly.

Signed-off-by: Hariom Chaturvedi <hariom4694@gmail.com>

- Added filebeat index patterns
- Added `evtxtoelk` in `docker-compose.yaml`
- Renamed winlogbeat pattern
